This theme is based on a _Jekyll_ theme with the same name.

### Settings

Custom settings are available in `.\lot\y\contrast\state.php` file.

 - Add custom link icons in the `icons` state.
 - Limit the maximum links displayed in site navigation by setting the `nav-show` state value as numbers to describe the
   limit.
 - There are two custom `skin` available: `contrast` and `minimal`.
 - To hide the site icons, set the `icons-show` state value to `false`.
 - To hide the site navigation, set the `nav-show` state value to `false`.
 - To hide the site title, set the `title-show` state value to `false`.

### Embeds

You can also embed a lot of stuff, for example from _YouTube_. To scale the video to full width use the
`<div class="embed"></div>` wrapper around the iframe. Use `<div class="large"></div>` wrapper to increase the width of
an image or iframe.